data.title: Meet the Orchestra MSO and James Morrison
data.meta_description: In May 2017 I took my 4yo to see world renowned trumpeter James Morrison and the Melbourne Symphony Orchestra perform a special Meet the Orchestra performance at the Arts Centre Melbourne. What a treat is was.
